<td valign="top" width="20%"><font face="verdana,trebuchet,sans-serif" color="black" style="font-size: 11px"><b>chakan</b>
<br>15 November 2003</font></td><td width="80%"><font><b>Earthdawn Minis</b>
<br>
<p>I found a store in Barcelona, that still has most of the Earthdawn Minis for sale.<p></p>They have 43 out of the 53 that I know of.<p></p>Their website is in Spanish, but they had no problem answering my emails back in English.  The shipping adds up, but in my opinion is worth it for the T'Skrang, Obsidiman and proper Troll figs...<p></p>The URL for the Heartbreaker section is as follows:<p></p>http://personal3.iddeo.es/juegossinfronteras/htbrkre.htm<p></p>You may want to add that to some list, as it may help new GMs get "authentic" ED minis.  Its ashame I won't be getting a complete set, as my wife only allowed me to pick up seven of the ones I need.<p></p>-Phil</p>
</font></td>
